	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Aug 3rd 2:16 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well, for starters I'm just gonna say that LowerGuk is a sweet place to lvl at, in less than 2 weeks i went from lvl 35 to lvl 40.. which I am presently...&nbsp;&nbsp;at lvl 35 your taking a chance and you will die alot, but I still die alot at lvl 40, but the loot is great down there... I mean 100p+ a night plus some sweet drops... my fav being the exe/cav/sage/sav grp cause lotsa grp stuff drops and most of the items are worth 200p or so... so it's a good place to go if u wanna start upgrading<br><br>Ok, my questions,  I just got Disarm and I have the skill up to 82 and I'm still yet to actually disarm somthing! like common here, what good is it anyways...<br>Next question is, Is 1hb really worth trainig? sure I got my 1hs and 2hs up to 200 already but I was wondering which skill I should bring up next... 1hb 2hb or piercing????.... I'm told there are some sweet 2h piercing weapons out there but I've never even heard of one yet...  If someone could tell me what skill is the most valuable and what is the easiest way to bring it up I'd like that... Actually, tell me that and also what weapons to buy to bring up the other skills (meaning some under 1k weapons that are real fast and bring the skill up quickly)<br><br>Well, sorry to say but I hafta stall my character for 8 months cause I hafta go to Colledge in September and account finished tonight... Hopefully in 8 months there will have been yet another sweet patch, besides the new one, and we pallies get some sweet 1hb or 2hb weapons palli only.... I can only pray<br><br>Seeya in 8 months questers<br>&nbsp;<br>Dethzary DethKiss<br>40th season<br><br>"The yellow snow on the other side always tastes better"</td></tr>
